    public interface ImageAnalyser<I extends Image<?,I>>
    An interface for objects that are able to perform analysis on images. The ImageAnalysers should not change the image; if you want to change the pixels, use an ImageProcessor instead.
    Author:
    Jonathon Hare (jsh2@ecs.soton.ac.uk)
